🎉 Shoutout to Winston for revolutionizing community engagement in HAX!

His brilliant work on the `hax party` command is transforming how developers connect with our ecosystem. What started as a simple CLI feature has become a powerful community onboarding tool.

🚀 **Winston's Contributions:**
• Implemented GitHub CLI integration for seamless repo management
• Added comprehensive documentation for new developers
• Fixed critical git author handling issues
• Created one-command setup for multiple HAX repositories

The `hax party` command now opens direct pathways to:
📚 Documentation (haxtheweb.org)
🎮 Interactive playground (hax.cloud) 
💬 Discord community
🎯 GitHub issues & contributions
🎓 HAX The Club (PSU student org)

**This is community-driven development at its finest.** Winston saw the friction points in developer onboarding and built elegant solutions that make contributing to HAX accessible and fun.

When students lead innovation, amazing things happen. 🌟

Ready to join the party? 
👉 `npm install @haxtheweb/create -g && hax party github`

Thank you Winston for making HAX more welcoming for everyone! 🙏

#OpenSource #CommunityFirst #StudentDevelopers #HAX #WebComponents #DeveloperExperience #PSU
